The '''Capital Terminal''' was one of the oldest still-functioning [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceports]] on the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic's]] [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Because of its woebegone nature and deep location, the port was often used by the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] as a means of covertly dispatching teams of [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] out into the wider [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy]].

